data.description: Welcome to your affordable home in Greeley, Colorado! This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence boasts not only a fantastic location but also an array of amenities for comfortable living and entertaining. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the fresh, new paint and updated flooring that create a bright and inviting atmosphere throughout the home. The open living and dining area is perfect for gatherings, with ample space to accommodate your loved ones. The modern kitchen is a true focal point, offering sleek countertops, contemporary cabinetry, and stainless steel appliances. Cooking enthusiasts will appreciate the functionality and style of this culinary haven. The master bedroom, offers a quiet retreat at the end of the day. Two additional bedrooms provide flexibility for family, guests, or the home office you've always dreamed of. But it's the outdoor space that truly sets this home apart. The large parking space out front, combined with a 1-car garage, ensures plenty of room for your vehicles and storage needs. Venture into the backyard, and you'll discover a sprawling oasis with a covered patio, ideal for savoring morning coffee or hosting summer BBQs. A storage shed adds extra convenience, providing space for your outdoor gear and tools. This charming property offers not just a house, but a lifestyle. Imagine the possibilities for gardening, outdoor play, or simply relaxing in the shade on a warm Colorado afternoon. Located in a sought-after Greeley neighborhood, you'll have easy access to schools, parks, shopping, and dining. The combination of a well-maintained interior, extensive outdoor space, and contemporary upgrades make this home a true treasure.
